find sticks between 3 and 6 feet long. Drill holes about 1/4 inch in diameter in each end.  Use string/cord/twine/wires/plarn to join ends.  Use octahedra and tetrahedra to build up complex modular structures for shelter, power generation along the rivers, and communication infrastructure.

